Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:19.88,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}就要坠入梦乡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:23.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}把什么放在了手边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.02,0:22:29.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}明明不想忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:31.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}却又无法想起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:35.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}时而浮现在记忆角落里的往日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:39.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}轻轻染上岁月的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:46.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}一纵即逝　渐行渐离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:55.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}气喘吁吁地奔跑又是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:23:01.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}愈是加快步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:05.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}就愈是畏惧停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.35,0:23:12.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}抚摸加速的心跳确认了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:20.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}侧耳倾听　那微弱的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:29.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}{\be5}却发现　天高海阔　直至未来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------TEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明个子那么小声音却好大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说「去死」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑  去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在嘀咕些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波之间的客人好像不要早餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小说家  弄得好像全是这边的错一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我们吃掉吧  那家伙的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不先空着肚子的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇的工作餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不止是芋艿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还放了蜥蜴什么的该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃蜥蜴？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讨厌她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…并不是讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是她说话的时候不仅直直地盯着你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且声音也大…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙居然背叛我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明没做工作餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要被彻先生责骂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多…芋艿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  她人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候在我身上发生了不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs36}「捆绑百选」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里？还是穿过这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要绑成龟甲缚却又绑不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然反被监禁的少女教…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我不会大叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么需要把我绑起来还塞住嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧  那篇小说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「温泉女服务员  满身泡沫的新人研修」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  其实不是什么人气小说家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何就是写不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么做都写不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不能让人共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为把自己关在旅馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能想出什么好题材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后获奖  想要一举逆转这个状况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就要满身泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了偿还眼前拖欠的住宿费
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次才想起写工口小说的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工口…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但连工口却都写不出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那个才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么灰心…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有才能这不是自己能判断的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…能拜托你一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不在大厅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷  你那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在做料理的中途消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和那个小说家的原稿的消失有关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪犯在这个旅馆里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}果然还是报警吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是讨厌我们了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}报警吗  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做了对绪花很过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}联络警察来调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}好  我去打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回东京去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}明白了  那么拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那趁这段时间再…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也没什么客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行全馆大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老板娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用忍耐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是这个旅馆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的我会全部好好教给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时声音那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这种时候也那么大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…有才能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我声音就那么大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…不能算小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么要写我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是在观察你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有偷看洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没有  真的  我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣什么的  我还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想变得闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  好好摩擦这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会闪耀的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要闪耀是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体有点疲惫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎丸先生  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…今天需要打扫么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  今天就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…我来查看下电灯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为老在意这种事  原稿才会丢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人无语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾旅馆果然只有垃圾女服务员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  为什么你出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你说过头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样就把你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样连这个老头也龟甲缚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能不可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要绑这么多人是不可能的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下  次郎丸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是谎言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为他很有名气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才对那些性骚扰睁一只眼闭一只眼的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙总是对料理挑三拣四的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘这次一定要报警…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}报警…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听客人亲口承认之前还不好判断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘不相信我说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  在那之前我们不能去怀疑客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怀疑…我们都亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷正要被龟甲缚的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这件事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是我们的车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁在驾驶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为在这种时候也不能打破常规
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才那么无能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能破壳而出…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快给我开门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊上啊  莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沥水豆腐皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为下个月的菜单如何  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不错  试着做一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎没什么紧张感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在车里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家面前装模作样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算欺骗大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那种事…早就被老板娘看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费别人的善意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我还是消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才不是善意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘说是因为工作才那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘才不会那么好心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家好不容易进入状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  客人  事实就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使注意到客人的真实情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能对其怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说如果你获奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也能收到付款  这样反而爽快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的事谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要获奖…不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不放弃要获奖的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性就永远存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人还是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是太威风了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那个才能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获奖什么的绝对不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎丸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  帮我拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快住…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子小时候的绰号是小河童
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三岁起就在游泳学校学习了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  去接菜子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很威风哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死都死不成  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么还在说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎丸先生有才能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我想变得闪耀」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是次郎丸先生写的小说的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我和民子和菜子登场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在浴室用拖布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清洗奇怪的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那篇小说  虽然工口…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:17:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却让我注意到了…连我自己都没注意到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明不是想工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却不甘心  想做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么会这样想 连我自己也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是次郎丸先生却告诉了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来我是想变得闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然不怎么了解小说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那一定是需要观察力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉了我不明白的事的次郎丸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的…是真正的小说家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎丸先生也开始在旅馆工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边偿还住宿费一边执笔争取获奖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在海边吃饭比较豪华
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好哦  少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不够意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大活跃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳的样子  很威风哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  那个没必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不啊  没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能好好教你女服务员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是游泳的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是有点自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小鱼比较搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你盛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}吃下去了吃下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的搞不懂她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伴  那孩子真的和皋月一个样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  次郎丸先生换好地方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说原本是放被褥的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那点程度还是让他忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电六  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花她会做好一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋只要适得其所也能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}「日本的旅馆  服务员教程 初级  时刻为客人着想」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在练习削皮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs36}除「去死」以外的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs36}不爽→有点太普通…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs36}别过来→伤害还不够…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs36}hobiron→ho=真是  bi=让人诧异到  ron=不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋…胚胎已经死亡的禽蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可食用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从生理上难以接受 意思也对的上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份努力  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这么拼命地讨厌  总觉得有点神清气爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是妈妈的不分场合的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不分场合的习惯是妈妈遗传的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs36}阿孝：\N没去送你对不起  绪花  加油！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在东京的时候总觉得这么交流是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.51,0:21:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到阿孝的邮件居然会这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「加油」…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里  加油到变得闪耀
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子非常受欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}是最任性的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}谁是「高原的少女」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别—吵—了
